// Common Utilities
Utilities [icon: tool] {
  Common Utility [icon: wrench]
}

// Connections
DB <> App, PAM, Notifier, QBO Webhooks, Stripe Accounting
QBO <> QBO Webhooks
Stripe <> Stripe Accounting
App <> PAM, Notifier, QBO Webhooks, Stripe Accounting

// PAM Connections
PAM Processing <> PAM Service Bus, PAM Storage, Check Rendering
PAM Printing <> PAM Processing
PAM Billing <> Stripe

// PDF Imaging Connections
Check Rendering <> PDFImaging
DynamicPDFRenderingEngine <> PDFRenderingServiceCommon
TemplatesQuickBooks <> PDFRenderingServiceCommon
PDFRenderingServiceCommon <> PDFImagingCommon

// Notifier Connections
Notifier Dispatch <> Notifier Service Bus
Notifier Service Bus <> Notifier Process
Notifier Process <> SendGrid

// QBO Connections
QBO Webhooks Dispatch <> QBO Webhooks Service Bus
QBO Webhooks Service Bus <> QBO Webhooks Process

